src_text: Icandelo lezemisebenzi nobungcali lamaphulo okulwa i-COVID-29 likhokelwa liQumrhu leSizwe eliDibeneyo lezeMisebenzi nezobuNtlola (i-NATJOINTS) kunye neSebe lezeMpil I-NATJOINTS liqumrhu eliquka amacandelo amaninzi lokuququzelela eliphantsi korhulumente elithi livuselelwe ukuze lilawule amaphulo amakhul I-COVID-19 NATJOINTS yenziwe ngamaqela azingcali aquka oosonzululwazi; ingcali zezempilo, iinjineli; abo bamele amaziko oLawulo lweeNtlekele zeSizwe; abacebisi bezomthetho; iziphathamandla ze-arhente zezokhuseleko nezogcino-mthetho zesizwe, kunye namaqela aphuma kumasebe ayinxalenye yentlanganisela yezoqoqosho nezempilo kunye neQumrhu labaLawuli-Jikelele boMzantsi Afrika (i-FOSAD).
trg_text: The COVID-19 NATJOINTS is built on work streams that comprise scientists; health specialists; engineers; representatives of the National Disaster Management centres; legal advisors; leadership of the country s security and law-enforcement agencies, and teams from departments that make up the economic and social clusters of the Forum of South African Directors-Genera NATJOINTS receives reports from different departments and submits proposals to Directors-General (DGs) to develop recommendations that are presented to the National Coronavirus Command Council (NCCC).

src_text: Ukwakha isiKhululo i-Deep Space Ground IKhabhinethi ivumile ukuba i-South African National Space Agency (i-SANSA) ityikitye isivumelwano sentsebenzisane ne-National Aeronautics and Space Administration (u-NASA) yakhe i-Deep Space Ground Statio Esi sikhululo, siza kwakhiwa eMatjiesfontein eNtshona Koloni, siza kuncedisa kwizipheke-pheke xa zisiya eNyangeni, ku-Mars nangaphay Esi sikhululo siza kuba yinxalenye yezi zikhululo zintathu zikhoyo zifana nesi: esinye sise-United States of America, esinye e-Spain size esinye sibe se-Australi Njengesikhululo sesine, siza kusebenzisana nezi zintathu zikhoyo sincedise ngobuxhaka-xhaka boncedo kumaphulo okuya emajuku-jukwin Esi sikhululo siza kusetyenziswa, silungiswe size sibe phantsi kolawulo lwe-SANS
